*3月22日，博科聖地武裝分子一夜之間殺害了至少23名查德士兵，查德的兩名消息来源當天稱，這似乎是伊斯蘭激進分子在查德境內進行的有史以來最致命的襲擊。突襲發生在[[查德湖|查德湖]]畔附近的当达拉鎮（Dangdala）。消息來源之一補充說，襲擊者被認為是從鄰國尼日爾越過邊界的。<ref>{{cite news |title=Boko Haram militants kill 23 Chad soldiers: security sources |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-chad-security/boko-haram-militants-kill-23-chad-soldiers-security-sources-idUSKCN1R3131 |accessdate=2020-04-26 |agency=Reuters |date=2019-03-22 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208145629/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-chad-security/boko-haram-militants-kill-23-chad-soldiers-security-sources-idUSKCN1R3131 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

*8月15日，在博爾諾州首府[[迈杜古里|迈杜古里]]郊區的一個村莊與伊斯蘭激進分子的槍戰中，三名奈及利亞士兵被殺。<ref>{{cite news |author1=Fergus Kelly |title=‘Boko Haram’ attacks Nigeria military base in Molai, near Maiduguri |url=https://www.thedefensepost.com/2019/08/15/nigeria-boko-haram-molai-maiduguri/ |accessdate=2020-04-25 |agency=The Defense Post |date=2019-08-15 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208152152/https://www.thedefensepost.com/2019/08/15/nigeria-boko-haram-molai-maiduguri/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

